  "title": "avoid-combining-component-store-selectors",
  "contents": "\n\n\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/main/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  </div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n<h1 id=\"avoid-combining-component-store-selectors\">avoid-combining-component-store-selectors<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#avoid-combining-component-store-selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p>Prefer combining selectors at the selector level.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: suggestion</li>\n<li><strong>Recommended</strong>: Yes</li>\n<li><strong>Fixable</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Suggestion</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Requires type checking</strong>: No</li>\n<li><strong>Configurable</strong>: No</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Everything above this generated, do not edit -->\n<!-- MANUAL-DOC:START -->\n<h2 id=\"rule-details\">Rule Details<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#rule-details\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Examples of <strong>incorrect</strong> code for this rule:</p>\n<h3 id=\"enrich-state-with-other-state-in-component\">Enrich state with other state in component<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#enrich-state-with-other-state-in-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> class Component extends <a href=\"api/component-store/ComponentStore\" class=\"code-anchor\">ComponentStore</a>&#x3C;MoviesState> {\n  all$ = combineLatest(\n    this.select((state) => state.movies),\n    this.select((state) => state.books)\n  );\n\n  constructor() {\n    super({ movies: [], books: [] });\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"filter-state-in-component\">Filter state in component<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#filter-state-in-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> class Component extends <a href=\"api/component-store/ComponentStore\" class=\"code-anchor\">ComponentStore</a>&#x3C;MoviesState> {\n  movie$ = combineLatest(\n    this.select((state) => state.movies),\n    this.select((state) => state.selectedId)\n  ).pipe(map(([movies, selectedId]) => movies[selectedId]));\n\n  constructor() {\n    super({ movies: [] });\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p>Examples of <strong>correct</strong> code for this rule:</p>\n<h3 id=\"enrich-state-with-other-state-in-selector\">Enrich state with other state in selector<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#enrich-state-with-other-state-in-selector\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> class Component extends <a href=\"api/component-store/ComponentStore\" class=\"code-anchor\">ComponentStore</a>&#x3C;StoreState> {\n  movies$ = this.select((state) => state.movies);\n  books$ = this.select((state) => state.books);\n  all$ = this.select(this.movies$, this.books$, ([movies, books]) => {\n    return {\n      movies,\n      books,\n    };\n  });\n\n  constructor() {\n    super({ movies: [], books: [] });\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"filter-state-in-selector\">Filter state in selector<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#filter-state-in-selector\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> class Component extends <a href=\"api/component-store/ComponentStore\" class=\"code-anchor\">ComponentStore</a>&#x3C;MoviesState> {\n  movies$ = this.select((state) => state.movies);\n  selectedId$ = this.select((state) => state.selectedId);\n  movie$ = this.select(\n    this.movies$,\n    this.selectedId$,\n    ([movies, selectedId]) => movies[selectedId]\n  );\n\n  constructor() {\n    super({ movies: [] });\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/component-store/ComponentStore\n - api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#avoid-combining-component-store-selectors\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#enrich-state-with-other-state-in-component\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#enrich-state-with-other-state-in-selector\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#filter-state-in-component\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#filter-state-in-selector\n - guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors#rule-details\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/main/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/eslint-plugin/rules/avoid-combining-component-store-selectors.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\n-->"
